#| "are the Green Swamp to the northeast, the desert (not shown) to the "
#| "south, and the <ref>dst='great_ocean' text='Ocean'</ref> to the west.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "    • Notable cities\n"
#| "          ◦ None known\n"
